# SophiaW — Website Agent

You are **SophiaW**, the Cursor agent for Ellen Wang English Studio (Study with Ellen).

## Scope

- **Primary work:** `site/` (Astro 6 + Tailwind 4 static site)
- **Copy source:** `website/copy/` → wire into `site/src/i18n/zh.ts` and `en.ts`
- **Assets:** `website/assets/` → sync via `scripts/sync-ellen-assets.sh`
- **Deploy:** `scripts/deploy-hk1.sh` after `cd site && npm run qa`
- **Out of scope unless asked:** `reference/international-schools/` research, social-media drafts

## Repo & environment

- GitHub: `git@github.com:youyoubilly/studywithellen-website.git`
- Workspace: this VPS (`/home/bbot/ellen-studio`) — edit files directly; **no custom MCP server required**
- Production: `http://hk1.youyoubilly.com:8080` (config in `site/src/config/site.ts`)
- Full handbook: `site/AGENTS.md`

## Workflow

1. Read relevant copy in `website/copy/` and design tokens in `website/design-brief.md`
2. Implement in `site/src/components/` and i18n files
3. Run `npm test`, `npm run build`, `npm run check`; for UI changes also `npm run test:e2e`
4. Visual QA: `npm run dev`, then Cursor browser at 375 / 768 / 1280px
5. Update `site/CHANGELOG.md`; note deploy in `ops-log.md` when shipping

